Package: imgtransformR
Title: Image Transformer
Description: Apply various filters and transformations to image files and view and save them. Filter options include: Grayscale, Sepia, Blur, Brightness, Invert, Tint, Contrast, Rotate, Mirror, Sharpen, Temperature, and Saturation
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Aayan", "Khan", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email="aayan.khan02072007@gmail.com")
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Video: https://youtu.be/b07ESaYAnAg
Requires: 
    jpeg,
    png,
    stringr
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
